</p></li></ol></prereq><section id="GUID-E4895B67-7FC1-4974-A5C8-D34725505879" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Required tools</title><ul id="UL_A32A562039FB485780CA65B069EE577C" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_55373F9DAE644089ABBC568E03CDE4FC" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Screwdriver Torx T20. 
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-EC9C24D5-D455-4022-B616-D7FEF4DE0A1A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Illustration</title><fig id="FIG_C01D5E6DAF3947439F96BC7462E442A2" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-2FF73991-BEA6-4E02-9A16-7A06CBBAAE41-low.png" id="IMAGE_FB8EAC8EE9B04707BF32BBC71F3D5E90" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-2FF73991-BEA6-4E02-9A16-7A06CBBAAE41-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="SECTION_DACE34B3D19943EF85419C55E3285A63" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to remove</title><table pgwide="1" id="TABLE_3B033A86E1FC4B4DB8FE5EB93DCAF4AF" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">If applicable: Disconnect the connector and remove the cable from the cable guide. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_DF1C4B11D612433E86537BDE74EEFD04" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-ACFC734D-505D-4673-9721-CF0735624193-low.png" id="IMAGE_738B2BE8177148D68B4D89433952A3B2" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-ACFC734D-505D-4673-9721-CF0735624193-low.png"/></fig><fig id="FIG_52F6C8EFD27A446DA860840D8C03DFC0" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-23840327-9F72-4682-8648-0E82966E9F85-low.png" id="IMAGE_146FAB9D3AD84A53AAA66FB636EA92AE" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-23840327-9F72-4682-8648-0E82966E9F85-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Remove 2 x 2 screws (left and right hand side). 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_2753BBEFF53C4389A627D4EFB54D0B56" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-19A1DDE2-BB10-493E-8F2A-A4490FD62BE4-low.png" id="IMAGE_629BA24B7A5A404782F463D968BA448D" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-19A1DDE2-BB10-493E-8F2A-A4490FD62BE4-low.png"/></fig><fig id="FIG_248917A542CB4651BF16D5906C2D0C29" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-02B24E6A-4706-4A5A-AA01-F0A41FAC64C4-low.png" id="IMAGE_04A9DFC27EDC45049735644238A0E68F" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-02B24E6A-4706-4A5A-AA01-F0A41FAC64C4-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the guide plate with melinex strip towards you. 
</p><note id="GUID-C4BD40C8-EB89-4AE9-9D95-FD18BDBF6EA2" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Do not bent the melinex guide strip. 
</p></note></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_16FDC1E56F124226844A6B7E3CFA93D7" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-2FF73991-BEA6-4E02-9A16-7A06CBBAAE41-low.png" id="IMAGE_A2BF05F20D11417488909FE350141B3F" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-2FF73991-BEA6-4E02-9A16-7A06CBBAAE41-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">If applicable: Remove the strip and place it on a new guide plate.
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-F498912D-8A5F-4549-AEA7-CAF033E2658F" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-83FF58E6-1FE2-481C-83D7-3D7435AB493E-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-83FF58E6-1FE2-481C-83D7-3D7435AB493E-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-234D70A5-41EC-40E2-9E43-4217D346F540" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to install</title><table pgwide="1" id="TABLE_F77204E29D3E4F6D8F3503958683C72F" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Install in reverse order. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Reconnect the Service jumper, exit SDS and press 'Restart' on the operator panel. 
